posts.message:
We just released Borium as Open source: http://getborium.com/

Borium is a lean queue job library to execute jobs in the background of web applications. It plays well with JavaScript, Python, Ruby, Bash.

It’s got two parts

The Server: In charge to keep the pending tasks organized and acts as the central task broker.

The Worker: Processing unit that run the actual tasks.
